disclaimer:
Zeus Music App is a music player that is based on YouTube.Just like any other music player, you can listen to your favorite music, search music, lyrics, albums and more, add to playlist, like songs. 
You can directly copy the YouTube Link of the Music you're Listening to. Zeus Music even allows you to download any music in mp3 format. 
You can Set Streaming Quality and also change the appearance of the app upto some extent. You can even play the music video of the song you're listening to. 
Zeus Music doesn't sell your any data to any third party or uses your data to show you ads based on that. 
Zeus Music is an app made for Educational Purpose, I do not suggest you to use it, but if you use then i am not responsible.
